EDUCATIONAL NOTICE:
This software is created for educational purposes to demonstrate Qt5 
cross-platform development and network programming concepts. It is intended 
for learning and research in controlled, authorized network environments only.

RESPONSIBLE USE:
Users must ensure they have proper authorization before capturing network 
traffic. Unauthorized network monitoring may be illegal in your jurisdiction. 
Always respect privacy and follow applicable laws and regulations.
